    "description": "玩家群（QQ）：626780712<br>这是《剑侠图》的官方玩家群，你可以在这里对我们刚刚发布的《剑侠图DEMO》提出建议，所有的反馈我们均会进行记录，并且以日更的形式对游戏进行优化与修改。希望在我们的共同努力下，能够让《剑侠图》以更加完整的状态面世。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1525570/extras/488cd854a031b84df0b2c5ac787e2f5a.poster.avif?t=1658221024\" width=544 height=146 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1525570/extras/488cd854a031b84df0b2c5ac787e2f5a.webm?t=1658221024\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1525570/extras/488cd854a031b84df0b2c5ac787e2f5a.mp4?t=1658221024\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>《剑侠图》是一款以近代历史中武侠为题材的模拟经营游戏。</strong></h2>作为盛世武林中人，体验多个地区，各种行业的生活，一幅纷繁多样的画卷将缓缓展现。游历江湖乃是吾辈之愿，无论蛮夷之地或锦绣之城，至此，踏上江湖之路。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1525570/extras/e6f8d72c1c5a48322b1c1bf13b390a99.poster.avif?t=1658221024\" width=544 height=146 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1525570/extras/e6f8d72c1c5a48322b1c1bf13b390a99.webm?t=1658221024\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1525570/extras/e6f8d72c1c5a48322b1c1bf13b390a99.mp4?t=1658221024\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>作为盛世武林中人，以建造门派为立足，在江湖中闯荡。玩家可以在荒野或城市获取资源进而发展自己的门派，体验江湖的爱恨情仇。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1525570/extras/73e55a42e8f913fae4b127c2c45a8588.poster.avif?t=1658221024\" width=544 height=146 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1525570/extras/73e55a42e8f913fae4b127c2c45a8588.webm?t=1658221024\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1525570/extras/73e55a42e8f913fae4b127c2c45a8588.mp4?t=1658221024\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >在《剑侠图》中，可以进行战略规划：</h2>资源获取，房屋建造，门派发展，通过不一样的策略以强大自身，玩家还可以体验种种生活，以不同的视角来审视江湖。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1525570/extras/3097444e1d0a3bdaf02380812c3b555a.poster.avif?t=1658221024\" width=544 height=146 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1525570/extras/3097444e1d0a3bdaf02380812c3b555a.webm?t=1658221024\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1525570/extras/3097444e1d0a3bdaf02380812c3b555a.mp4?t=1658221024\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>这是一个“提倡武术的精神”的世界。习武意在：小则健身保家，大则为国效力。武侠的品德和心胸，应是光明磊落，疾恶如仇；扶困济危，赴汤蹈火；维护良善，伸张正义、维护社会安定。如果是非不分，恃强凌弱，违背侠义道的话，人人得而诛之。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1525570/extras/06ee8a2646f0686143b71c6a8d16ac29.poster.avif?t=1658221024\" width=544 height=146 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1525570/extras/06ee8a2646f0686143b71c6a8d16ac29.webm?t=1658221024\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1525570/extras/06ee8a2646f0686143b71c6a8d16ac29.mp4?t=1658221024\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>这样的故事涉及各个地区，各种行业的生活，向玩家展示一幅幅广阔的纷繁多样的社会生活画面。这些人物他们有的出身农户，有的是金门绣户，有的生于楚馆，有的是杏林世家，有的是市井小民……每一个人物的出现都有着对应背景和故事的展现。在这段时期武林各种流派之间的江湖之争，引得各路英雄齐出。乃是武术大兴，民族强盛之盛世。",
